These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Transport: skateboard, airplane, roller, van
1. Transport:airplane is in an odd position##4
2. Transport:van is between Transport:skateboard and Transport:airplane##2
3. Transport:van is on the right of Transport:skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Transport   | skateboard | van | airplane | roller |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Game: snooker, backgammon, canasta, whist
1. Game:snooker is on the left of Game:whist##1
2. Game:backgammon is in an odd position##4
3. Game:backgammon is on the left or right of Game:snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Game   | backgammon | snooker | whist | canasta |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
