2. Cigar:old-henry is in an odd position##4
3. Cigar:chaman is between Cigar:bolivar and Cigar:dunhill##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | old-henry | bolivar | chaman | dunhill |

