.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Cigar: oliveros, havana, aristoff, ritmeester
1. Cigar:havana == Cigar:havana##1
2. Cigar:ritmeester is on the left or right of Cigar:aristoff##3
3. Cigar:aristoff is on the far left or far right##3
4. Cigar:oliveros is in an even position##4
5. Cigar:ritmeester is on the left of Cigar:havana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | ritmeester | havana | oliveros |

